      "id": "ex_s3_3_1",
      "question": "數據：2, 4, 6, 8, 10，求變異數",
      "answer": "$8$",
      "solution": "平均數：$\\bar{x} = \\frac{2+4+6+8+10}{5} = 6$\n\n$s^2 = \\frac{(2-6)^2 + (4-6)^2 + (6-6)^2 + (8-6)^2 + (10-6)^2}{5}$\n\n$= \\frac{16 + 4 + 0 + 4 + 16}{5} = \\frac{40}{5} = 8$",
      "difficulty": "medium",
      "type": "calc",
      "tags": ["變異數"]
