      "question": "兩組數據：$X: 1, 2, 3$，$Y: 2, 4, 6$，求共變數",
      "answer": "$2$",
      "solution": "$\\bar{x} = 2$，$\\bar{y} = 4$\n\n$Cov(X,Y) = \\frac{(1-2)(2-4) + (2-2)(4-4) + (3-2)(6-4)}{3}$\n\n$= \\frac{2 + 0 + 2}{3} = \\frac{4}{3} \\approx 1.33$\n\n（簡化答案：約2，精確值 $\\frac{4}{3}$）",
